Plot outline:
The Monty Pyton team tells the life, death and resurrection (?) of Brian from Nazareth, an unwilling prophet who wants to free his land from the oppression of Rome. When Brian covers a huge wall with the writing &quot;ROMANI ITE DOMUM&quot; (Romans go home), a local revolutionary group begins to take him seriously...
